data.description: HIGHEST AND BEST BY 3PM MONDAY 4/22. This SPECTACULAR Wyandotte home is ready for the new owner!! Walk in through the charming covered porch into a light and bright living room with gorgeous floors and beautiful historic features. Through the open concept archway you will find a formal dining area that leads to a cute kitchen with lots of storage. There is a bedroom on the main floor that could be used as a primary bedroom and a half bath that has been nicely updated. Upstairs you will find two generously sized bedrooms and an updated full bath. Downstairs is an unfinished basement with lots of potential, separate laundry area and includes a finished gorgeous full bath. Basement has been waterproofed and has a sump pump. Furnace and A/C 2021. Outside you will find a HUGE backyard and a covered porch/patio area perfect for entertaining. BATVD
